snippet.title: Command & Conquer Red Alert 3: Uprising Launch Trailer
snippet.description: Conquer four new campaigns as the Red Alert 3 saga continues in Command & Conquer Red Alert 3: Uprising!   Featuring 12 new units, the new Commanders Challenge, 30 minutes of HD cinematics starring Malcolm McDowell, Nature Boy Ric Flair, Gemma Atkinson, Holly Valance, and many more, Uprising is Available NOW at the EA Store, Direct2Drive, GameStop, and your favorite digital download services worldwide!
